### Installation

1. Download the latest `clipboard-mcp.exe` from the [Releases page](link).
2. Save it to a permanent location (e.g., `C:\mcp\clipboard-mcp.exe`).
3. Add the following to your Claude Desktop config (`%APPDATA%\Claude\claude_desktop_config.json`):

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "clipboard-manager": {
      "command": "C:\\mcp\\clipboard-mcp.exe"
    }
  }
}